[Episode 24]

5
00:00:36,330 --> 00:00:37,790
to enjoy beautiful clouds

6
00:00:38,020 --> 00:00:39,310
and stars.

7
00:00:53,830 --> 00:00:54,490
Sir,

8
00:00:54,870 --> 00:00:56,070
everything is ready.

9
00:00:56,790 --> 00:00:57,920
Time to get changed.

10
00:01:14,110 --> 00:01:14,830
Congratulations.

11
00:01:14,830 --> 00:01:16,289
Wish you a long and happy marriage.

12
00:01:16,289 --> 00:01:17,120
I look forward to hearing the patter of tiny feet.

13
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:18,910
Young Master Tanshu, congratulations.

14
00:01:18,910 --> 00:01:19,590
Young Master Tanshu,

15
00:01:19,590 --> 00:01:20,650
congratulations.

16
00:01:59,470 --> 00:02:00,670
Distinguished

17
00:02:00,670 --> 00:02:01,400
guests,

18
00:02:01,550 --> 00:02:02,710
welcome to the wedding

19
00:02:02,710 --> 00:02:03,830
of Mr. Shen Tanshu

20
00:02:03,830 --> 00:02:05,560
and Miss Feng Yuqing.

21
00:02:05,590 --> 00:02:08,229
Let's applaud for the couple together.

22
00:02:08,250 --> 00:02:09,729
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

23
00:02:35,270 --> 00:02:36,440
Next, let's...

24
00:02:42,230 --> 00:02:42,790
Sir!

25
00:02:43,870 --> 00:02:47,130
Young Master Tanqian and his men are fighting their way in!

26
00:02:51,110 --> 00:02:52,190
What on earth happened?

27
00:02:52,190 --> 00:02:54,240
I heard Hidekawa Kojima and the Yamato Chamber of Commerce's members

28
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,770
were killed by the Volunteer Group's members.

29
00:02:55,770 --> 00:02:58,570
They also found a lot of opium and cultural relics.

30
00:03:03,300 --> 00:03:04,630
The wedding continues.

31
00:03:08,470 --> 00:03:09,600
Guard the gate.

32
00:03:09,830 --> 00:03:10,360
Yes.

33
00:03:21,230 --> 00:03:22,350
Mr. Shen Tanshu,

34
00:03:23,150 --> 00:03:26,750
will you marry Miss Feng Yuqing

35
00:03:27,910 --> 00:03:28,670
and love her,

36
00:03:29,030 --> 00:03:29,870
comfort her,

37
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:30,850
respect her,

38
00:03:30,870 --> 00:03:31,730
and protect her

39
00:03:32,760 --> 00:03:34,350
like you love yourself?

40
00:03:34,860 --> 00:03:37,040
In health or sickness,

41
00:03:37,430 --> 00:03:38,750
in wealth or poverty,

42
00:03:38,970 --> 00:03:40,760
will you a-always be loyal to her

43
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:42,170
until you die?

44
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:46,700
Yes.

45
00:03:47,990 --> 00:03:49,030
Miss Feng Yuqing,

46
00:03:49,790 --> 00:03:53,350
will you marry... Mr. Shen Tanshu?

47
00:03:57,110 --> 00:03:58,110
Miss Feng Yuqing?

48
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:00,400
Miss Feng Yuqing?

49
00:04:11,750 --> 00:04:12,550
Yes.

50
00:04:14,550 --> 00:04:15,670
Now, Mr. Shen, please

51
00:04:15,670 --> 00:04:18,070
put the wedding ring on the bride's finger.

52
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,150
Mingzhao,

53
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,590
we grew up together.

54
00:05:08,290 --> 00:05:09,550
Don't force me to do it.

55
00:05:09,790 --> 00:05:11,450
Sorry, Young Master Tanqian.

56
00:05:11,530 --> 00:05:12,990
I have to protect Mr. Shen.

57
00:05:41,909 --> 00:05:42,680
Tanshu,

58
00:05:43,080 --> 00:05:44,550
how have you been?

59
00:05:45,190 --> 00:05:46,460
It's been half a year

60
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:48,240
since we got married.

61
00:05:49,030 --> 00:05:51,760
I want to tell you something through this letter.

62
00:05:52,710 --> 00:05:53,810
I have

63
00:05:54,350 --> 00:05:55,350
a lovely twin sister.

64
00:05:55,350 --> 00:05:56,480
Her name is Yuji.

65
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,400
She is now studying in Japan.

66
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:01,580
I still haven't told her about our marriage.

67
00:06:01,950 --> 00:06:04,750
I hope I can introduce you to her as soon as possible

68
00:06:05,150 --> 00:06:06,910
to let her know that I love you.

69
00:06:07,710 --> 00:06:08,510
Yuqing.

70
00:06:10,690 --> 00:06:12,750
In this life, I only hope my loved ones

71
00:06:13,020 --> 00:06:14,630
can be happy.

72
00:06:15,230 --> 00:06:16,590
Then I'll be satisfied.

73
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:27,200
Yuqing.

74
00:06:32,070 --> 00:06:33,400
Thank you for loving me.

75
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,370
Can you... Can you forgive me?
